git ​

1,git长名称解决--Filename too long ​

git config --global core.longpaths true

2, git warning: LF will be replaced by CRLF ​

git config --global core.autocrlf true

3,git分支命名main ​

找到user下的git-config文件添加
[init]
	defaultBranch = main
